pypickupbot - A simple IRC pickup bot written in Python
=======================================================

A script that encourages people to gather on IRC with the purpose of playing a
game with captain-picked teams on predetermined game modes.


Dependencies
------------

pypickupbot is written in Python, so doesn't need compiling. You will however
need the following dependencies at runtime:

  * Python 2.6 or higher Python 2
  * Twisted, the more recent the better


Setting up
----------

All you need to know and do is in the quick setup guide in the quick setup
guide(INSTALL.html). If for some reason you can't open html files, consult the
following files:

doc/quick/config.rst
doc/quick/usage.rst
